{"tid":1302270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣普及教育] 關於71立法會衝擊：我們應否要求撤控? Video 版","createTime":"2019-07-10T01:41:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T03:03:58.000Z","uid":1806,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2874dce3c819b1dfb55741f84fbde3abda73b51a","tid":1302270,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T01:41:53.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲好, 有絲打去為一系列圖的&lt;&lt;關於71立法會衝擊：我們應否要求撤控&gt;&gt;配音變成一個video版<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iOdCIVHhW-Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiOdCIVHhW-Y&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8CvjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=6e161f9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iOdCIVHhW-Y</a><br />\n<br />\n希望透過將一系列由文宣group既圖變成影片更易收看<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由絲打聲音導航，為你尋找答案，了解因由<br />\n<br />\nCredit to: <br />\nPictures: #文宣組 反送中印刷稿件大合集@TG<br />\nBackground Music: QUIET'S THEME (INSTRUMENTAL)<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲要加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 覺得有用就幫推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有仲有, 今日放榜, 祝各位考生可以入到自己所想既學系, 繼續追尋理想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">毋忘7大訴求</span></strong>, 第6同7項係近日發生同提出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 徹底撤回修例<br />\n2. 收回暴動定義<br />\n3. 撤銷至今對所有抗爭者控罪<br />\n4. 徹底追究警隊濫權<br />\n5. 實行真雙普選<br />\n6.要求永不落實「社會信用評分系統」<br />\n7.要求移除全港「多功能智慧燈柱」<br />\n<br />\n順度幫其他巴絲重要資訊forward 下D Links:<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">7.10 - TVB港姐 - <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1300556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/1300556</a><br />\n7.10 - 麥小姐追思會 ＠ 中環愛丁堡廣場 - 19:00~22:30<br />\n7.11 - 梁烈士公眾告別禮 - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8CvjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=7e80a854\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/leung711</a><br />\n7.11 - 油尖旺區議會夢遊 - <a href=\"http://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_dc711&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8CvjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=beb81355\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/ytm_dc711</a><br />\n7.12 - 光復港大 守衛我城 - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2S6Lw1T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2S6Lw1T&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8CvjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=7ba53b07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2S6Lw1T</a><br />\n7.13 - 光復上水 - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/32eEvRm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F32eEvRm&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8CvjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=dee58b86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/32eEvRm</a><br />\n7.14 - 沙田區大遊行 - <a href=\"http://t.me/st7142019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fst7142019&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8CvjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=8cf76ef9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/st7142019</a><br />\n7.28 - 將軍澳遊行 - <a href=\"http://t.me/tko728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftko728&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8CvjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=3f67f852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/tko728</a><br />\n隨時 - 抵制TVB - <a href=\"http://t.me/noTVBteam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FnoTVBteam&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8CvjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=48494ed1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/noTVBteam</a><br />\n隨時 - 美國聯署 人權民主法案 - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2XOf0aj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XOf0aj&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8CvjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=9e7e0b5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2XOf0aj</a></span></em>"},{"pid":"9fb8443b2a5516a70b96d22cf86269e80f9832cf","tid":1302270,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T01:43:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=